  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5e5cb7818a76e926.jpg?v=1782528066\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Last week while I was up in San Francisco for a quick day trip, I was able to check out the new <a href=\"http://www.colorfactory.co/\">Color Factory</a> and it was AMAZING. It just opened today and I highly recommend you go and reserve tickets! I took my friend Pamelyn from <a href=\"https://www.basheryandco.com/\">Bashery &amp; Co</a> and met up with <a href=\"http://instagram.com/alishylishy\">Alisha</a> and some friends for the fun.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0b-.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/18112209e403e736.jpg?v=1782528069\">\n</img></a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0c-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ab313fb8f5c2eed2.jpg?v=1782528072\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0d-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aa5ce73290e4041c.jpg?v=1782528075\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0e-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a19d22d457ffcd3b.jpg?v=1782528078\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0f-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/61d61d91c0dad9ef.jpg?v=1782528080\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0g-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c9a14ab6e1dc7f1f.jpg?v=1782528083\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0h-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fe958c211b9bde46.jpg?v=1782528086\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0i-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/87fcec79cd836609.jpg?v=1782528089\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0j-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/545b27f7c7cc2fc8.jpg?v=1782528091\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0k-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6cb1a7df35c48a76.jpg?v=1782528094\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0l-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3d53dd7a9abd2377.jpg?v=1782528097\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0m-14.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/29fa7a518dd77050.jpg?v=1782528100\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0n-15.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0c1861dd6d34d3ac.jpg?v=1782528103\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>I had to<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vUSyqPgdWGA\"> vlog the experience</a>, as it was everything you would imagine it to be and more.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Photos by <a href=\"http://lishcreative.com/\">LISH Creative</a> - You can see Alisha's post <a href=\"http://lishcreative.com/blog/2017/7/28/inside-the-color-factory-in-san-francisco\">here</a>, which includes a fun video. We are already planning a trip back as there is a map we picked up at the end that shows 17 other activations throughout the city, including colorful murals that will only be up for a limited amount of time!</p><p>There are a couple sneak peeks at the next Fresh Squeezed Fashion Tees, which will be available to subscribers on August 9 through Aug 14! </p><p>Also, I am SUPER EXCITED to share that I will be teaching in the UK for the first time in late October with <a href=\"http://birdsofafeather.uk.com/workshops\">Birds of a Feather at Chateau Impney!</a> It will be a really fun-filled weekend - come join us!</p>"
}